export var myIndexOf=function myIndexOf(hairetu,zokusei,key){var hensuu=-1;if(zokusei==="kanji"){hairetu.map(function(comp,index){if(comp.Kanji===key){hensuu=index;}});}else if(zokusei==="kata"){hairetu.map(function(comp,index){if(comp.kata===key){hensuu=index;}});}else if(zokusei==="eng"){hairetu.map(function(comp,index){if(comp.eng===key){hensuu=index;}});}return hensuu;};
